eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A 911 TELEPHONE OUTAGE EMERGENCY FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Marion, FL; AT 07:48 PM ON NOV 14, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 08:48 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: Marion County & Ocala 911 emergency phone systems have been repaired and have returned to normal working conditions. You can now CALL 911 to report an emergency and seek medical attention. The text to 911 service is always an option for reporting an emergency to the 911 communication center.
